TITLE: Episode 73 - The Vixens Meet a Right-Wing Extremist (featuring Carey Wedler)
DESCRIPTION: Jessie and Maddie sit down with Carey Wedler. Carey talks about she got labeled “right wing” and her frustrations with ever changing definitions of words and how important it is to move away from labels.
